'''Eärnil''' ([[Quenya|Q]], a contracted form of [[Eärendil]], pron. {{IPA|[eˈarnil]}}) can refer to:
* [[Eärnil I]], thirteenth [[Kings of Gondor|King]] of [[Gondor]] and the second of its [[Ship-king]]s.
* [[Eärnil II]], thirty-second King of Gondor, who won the [[Battle of the Camp]].
